intelligence in Kigali, has been transferred to the 305th Brigade
where he will be the army deputy commander for the
Gitarama-Kibuye region.
</P>
<P>
A Rwandan government spokesman described the military
reshuffle as "normal and usual administrative changes" designed
to "make things work better". 
