Act was signed on May 27.
</P>
<P>
The defense ministers discussed the development in
Bosnia-Herzegovina, military-to-military cooperation and nuclear
transparency in an effort to bring concrete substance to their
commitment to build a lasting peace in the Euro-Atlantic area.
