1543.86 from previous close of 1540.00.
</P>
<P>
The BSE-200 and the us dollar index were quoted up at 346.41
and 146.23 points compared with the previous close of 345.72 and
145.64 respectively.
</P>
<P>
Foreign institutional investors, who had been keeping aloof
from the market in the light of continuous rupee downslide to its
all-time low, suddenly became active today and bought heavily in
the market.
</P>
<P>
Operators were confused by the political happenings with no
clear indication on who would form government at the Center and
preferred to stay away from making any commitments.  
</P>
