Search and rescue experts from the Asia-Pacific region also
participated as observers.
</P>
<P>
Highlight of the annual event is the long-range exercise, to be
held Thursday in the South China Sea to test the alerting,
coordination, communications facilities and the search and rescue
techniques of various participants, said a spokesman for CAD.
</P>
<P>
