international forums was in accordance with the United Nations
resolution so as not to contravene the stand taken by other
pro-Palestine countries, he added.
</P>
<P>
He said though Malaysia supported the Palestinians in seeking a
peaceful settlement to their cause, it did not provide military
aid but helped rebuild their economy and infrastructure facilities
destroyed during the war.  
