<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 3 (Xinhua) -- The death toll in the coal-mine
explosion at the Zyryanovskaya mine in the Kemerovo region of
Russia, rose to 67 Tuesday night, the Itar-Tass news agency
reported today.
</P>
<P>
Rescue workers had located the bodies of 65 miners and
excavated 45 of them with 43 having been identified.
</P>
<P>
