Sysuyev arrived in Novokuznetsk Tuesday night and worked at the
explosion-hit Zyryanovskaya coal-mine till midnight.
</P>
<P>
Kemerovo regional governor Anan Tuleyev announced today on
local radio that the conclusive information about causes of the
accident would not be available before Thursday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 129 coal-miners died in accidents in the region's
coal industry in 1996, the report said. 
</P>
