<DOCNO> XIE19971203.0184 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-12-03 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Securities Markets Promote Enterprise Reform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 3 (Xinhua) -- China's securities markets have
expedited state enterprise reform by functioning as a channel for
fund-raising and transforming the management modes of listed
companies.
</P>
<P>
A total of 181 companies, or 35 percent of 512 key state
enterprises, have been so far listed on the nation's stock
markets, with some 50 percent of 120 trial state enterprise groups
also gaining listings.
</P>
<P>
"This serves as a clear indication that China's fledgling
securities markets have done their share in raising funds for
cash-strapped state enterprises and prompting them to introduce
management practices in line with the market economy," according
to one economist.
</P>
<P>
Between 1993 and last June, the markets enabled the state
sector to raise 41.5 billion yuan in funds for 285 key state- or
province-level projects, as well as 25.6 billion yuan for 165
technological renovation projects.
</P>
<P>
The markets have also promoted the efficient use of social
resources by expediting mergers and acquisitions of state
enterprises, in addition to revitalizing state ventures with cash
shortfalls, but good market potential. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19971203.0185 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-12-03 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chronology of CHT Peace Process (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
1993
</P>
<P>
May 22 -- 3rd meeting between the BNP government and PCJSS at
Khagrachhari Circuit House.
</P>
<P>
Jul.14 -- 4th meeting between the BNP government and PCJSS at
Khagrachhari Circuit House.
</P>
<P>
Sept.18 -- 5th meeting between the BNP government and PCJSS at
Khagrachhari circuit House.
</P>
<P>
Nov.24 -- 6th meeting between the BNP government and PCJSS at
Khagrachhari circuit House.
</P>
<P>
1994
</P>
<P>
Feb.15-22 -- 1st batch of 1,841 tribal refugees returned home
from Tripura state of India.
</P>
<P>
May 5 -- 7th meeting between the BNP government and PCJSS at
Khagrachhari circuit House.
</P>
<P>
Jun.4 -- The BNP government formed a sub-committee headed by
Rashed khan Menon. A meeting between the sub-committee and the
PCJSS held at Dudukchhari in Khagrachhari district.
</P>
<P>
Jul.10 -- 2nd meeting between the sub-committee and the PCJSS
held at Dudukchhari.
</P>
<P>
Aug.28 -- 3rd meeting between the sub-committee and the PCJSS
at Dudukchhari.
</P>
<P>
dec.26 -- 4th meeting between the sub-committee and the PCJSS
held at Dudukchhari.
