by saying that the company will rapidly increase its presence in
the country over the next 10-20 years.
</P>
<P>
Trotman said Ford plans to export components and vehicles from
China to other parts of the world, and will help China become an
important part of the worldwide motor vehicle industry.
</P>
<P>
