anti-constitution agreement" with the leaders of the tribals in
the Chittagong Hill Tracts (CHT), sources from the BNP said today.
</P>
<P>
The Bangladeshi government signed the historic peace agreement
with tribal rebels Tuesday after seven rounds of talks between the
government and the Chittagong Hill Tracks' tribal leaders.
</P>
