treaty, the BNP is likely to announce its action programs today,
local press reports predicted.
</P>
<P>
The BNP meeting reviewed the current political developments,
and called for greater unity of all the nationalist and patriotic
forces "to save the sovereignty and independence of the country."
</P>
<P>
A review committee to examine the legal aspects of the accord
was formed at the meeting, the sources said.  
