<HEADLINE> China's Top Three Areas of Foreign-Funded Businesses in Exports </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 3 (Xinhua) -- Following is a table showing
China's top three areas of foreign-funded businesses in terms of
export volume in the first eight months this year, according to
statistics released by China's General Administration of Customs:
</P>
