as the United States coach through the 1998 World Cup,
U.S. federation president Alan Rothenberg announced in Chicago on
Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The announcement came despite Rothenberg's unwillingness to
endorse Sampson's contract expired on November 16, when the
Americans finished World Cup qualifying one point behind leader
Mexico.
</P>
<P>
