<HEADLINE> UNSCOM Chairman to Visit Iraq This Weekend </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, December 2 (Xinhua) -- The Chairman of the
United Nations Special Commission (UNSCOM) Richard Butler would
visit Iraq this weekend, UN spokesman Fred Eckhard announced
today.
</P>
<P>
Butler, who heads the UNSCOM in charge of destroying Iraq's
weapons of mass destruction, had originally planned to fly to
Iraq in early November on a regular two-month visit. But the
